# https://example.org/story/action#hasPurpose
<https://example.org/story/action#hasPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/action#hasPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://example.org/story/action#Action> .
<https://example.org/story/action#hasPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/story/action#hasPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Why the agent performed the action (textual description)."@en .
<https://example.org/story/action#hasPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has purpose"@en .
# 
# https://example.org/story/place#hasFoundationDate
<https://example.org/story/place#hasFoundationDate> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasFoundationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://example.org/story/place#Place> .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasFoundationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasFoundationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "When the place was established. String because fictional dates don't always fit xsd:date."@en .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasFoundationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has foundation date"@en .
# 
# https://example.org/story/place#hasPopulation
<https://example.org/story/place#hasPopulation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasPopulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://example.org/story/place#Settlement> .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasPopulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger> .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasPopulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Number of inhabitants. Only makes sense for settlements."@en .
<https://example.org/story/place#hasPopulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has population"@en .
# 
# https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://example.org/story/plot#Chapter> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#positiveInteger> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The ordinal number of a chapter within the story."@en .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasChapterNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has chapter number"@en .
# 
# https://example.org/story/plot#hasPublicationDate
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasPublicationDate> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasPublicationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://example.org/story/plot#NarrativeWork> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasPublicationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasPublicationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The real-world date the narrative work was published."@en .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasPublicationDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has publication date"@en .
# 
# https://example.org/story/plot#hasTextSummary
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTextSummary> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTextSummary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTextSummary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A textual summary. No domain restriction for the same reason as hasTitle."@en .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTextSummary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has text summary"@en .
# 
# https://example.org/story/plot#hasTitle
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTitle> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The title of a story, section, or narrative work. No domain restriction because both NarrativeContainer and NarrativeWork can have titles."@en .
<https://example.org/story/plot#hasTitle> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has title"@en .
