<http://purl.org/meo/God> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "God"@en .
# 
# http://purl.org/meo/Immortal
<http://purl.org/meo/Immortal> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
