<http://purl.org/meo/Immortal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An individual that does not die of natural death. Some immortals may die from wounds inflicted to them by violence or accident (like Elves), but some are truly eternal, like the Ainur)."@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Immortal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "immortal"@en .
# 
# http://purl.org/meo/Lócë
