<http://purl.org/meo/Lócë> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Evil and powerful monster."@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Lócë> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dragon"@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Lócë> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lócë"@qya .
# 
