<http://purl.org/meo/Maia> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The Maiar (plural form of Maia) are Ainur who entered Arda and serve the Valar."@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Maia> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Beautiful"@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Maia> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Maia"@qya .
# 
# http://purl.org/meo/Mortal
