<http://purl.org/meo/Quendë> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The Quendi (plural form of Quendë) are the first born of the Children of Ilúvatar, the Elves. They are named thus because they were the only ones who spoke when they first appeared, before Men and Dwarves came to be. They are more often called the Eldar."@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Quendë> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Elf"@en .
