<http://purl.org/meo/Quendë> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Firstborn"@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Quendë> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "one that speaks"@en .
# 
